POST /api/profile – create profile
Body:

{
  "goal": "Lose Weight",
  "preferences": ["Vegetarian"],
  "availabilityPerWeek": 3,
  "dietaryRestrictions": ["Gluten-free"]
}


Returns 201 with { message: "Profile completed.", profile }

GET /api/profile/me – read my profile (404 if none)

PUT /api/profile – update profile (any field)
Returns 200 with { message: "Profile updated. A new personalized plan is ready.", profile }

GET /api/plan/week?start=YYYY-MM-DD – fetch weekly plan (generates if missing)
